li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">the SEC has a pretty strong case un=
der basic, long-established US securities law; and</li>=09<li style=3D"marg=
in-bottom: 5px;">the SEC=E2=80=99s answer to Coinbase=E2=80=99s question of=
 =E2=80=9Cokay well how do we comply with the law and operate a US crypto e=
